connects the engines to the rotor, so to handle

00:01:12.540 --> 00:01:16.440
it the transmission would need to be big and
heavy, and that’s a no-no.

00:01:16.440 --> 00:01:20.380
Engineers could use shorter blades and add
more of them, but then the hub in the middle

00:01:20.380 --> 00:01:22.570
